extends layout


block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em WebCafe], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Tables:] !{data.table_count}
      li #[strong Table Status Free:] !{data.table_status_free_count}
      li #[strong Table Status Busy before lunch:] !{data.table_status_busy_before_lunch_count}
      li #[strong Table Status Busy before lunch:] !{data.table_status_busy_after_lunch_count}
      li #[strong Menu Dish:] !{data.dish_count}
      li #[strong Waiters:] !{data.waiters_count}

